ZH: 他非常好学，每天晚上都会认真读书。
EN: He is very eager to learn and studies diligently every night.

ZH: 她的好学精神让她在班上成为了学霸。
EN: Her eagerness to learn has made her the top student in the class.

ZH: 我们要学习从好学的人身上汲取经验。
EN: We should learn from people who are eager to learn.

ZH: 他们一直以来都表现出非常好学的态度。
EN: They have always shown a great eagerness to learn.

ZH: 学习应该是一种好学的心态，而不只是为了得到好成绩。
EN: Studying should be approached with an eagerness to learn rather than just to achieve good grades.

ZH: 我们应该鼓励孩子们发展好学的习惯。
EN: We should encourage children to develop a love for learning.

ZH: 在知识的世界中，好学是成功的基石。
EN: In the world of knowledge, eagerness to learn is the foundation of success.

ZH: 他天生就有一种好学的天赋。
EN: He has a natural talent for learning.

ZH: 不断学习，不断进步，是好学者的信条。
EN: Constant learning and improvement is the creed of a eager learner.

ZH: 这个班级里谁都无法比得上她的好学精神。
EN: Nobody in this class can match her eagerness to learn.

ZH: 他对新事物总是保持着好学的态度。
EN: He always approaches new things with eagerness to learn.

ZH: 我的好学精神使我能够在职场上不断进步。
EN: My eagerness to learn allows me to constantly improve in my career.

ZH: 每位老师都希望有一群好学的学生。
EN: Every teacher hopes to have a group of eager learners.

ZH: 好学不只是为了知识，更是为了提升自己。
EN: Eagerness to learn is not only for acquiring knowledge but also for self-improvement.

ZH: 他用好学的态度征服了所有困难。
EN: He conquered all difficulties with his eagerness to learn.

ZH: 她的好学让她成为了领导者的宠儿。
EN: Her eagerness to learn has made her the favorite of leaders.

ZH: 学无止境，好学者能够乐享学习的过程。
EN: Learning is endless, and eager learners can enjoy the process of learning.

ZH: 我们应该时刻保持好学的心态。
EN: We should always maintain an eagerness to learn.

ZH: 好学是一种习得的本领，需要不断的培养。
EN: Eagerness to learn is a skill that needs to be constantly cultivated.

ZH: 只有好学的人才能够不断提升自己。
EN: Only those who are eager to learn can constantly improve themselves.
